{"tid":1696602,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"12k拉恐怖份子頭目落水，一齊做嘢啦！","createTime":"2019-11-06T09:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T09:48:12.000Z","uid":107577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f7a4c2c155180a19a7086aebe95dc2ac508abb3a","tid":1696602,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:12:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>眾籌啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />眾籌啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\nSorry各位，又係我。香港日日比人恐怖襲擊，真係又心痛又憤怒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋要拉恐怖份子首領落水，可以點做啊？宜家機會嚟啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊籌旗比香港民意研究所，佢哋會出一份民意研究：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&quot; 你有幾支持或者反對美國以《香港人權及民主法案》或者其他法案, 去制裁香港警務處處長, 以表明佢要為所有違規濫用暴力嘅警員負責?  &quot;</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n到時就有以下三大效果：<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><br />\n1.向香港市民及外國宣傳《香港人權及民主法案》及製造有利其通過的氛圍<br />\n2.震懾警隊高層及其背後勢力，有機會令其士氣低落。<br />\n3.給予美國施力點，避免美國要制裁時陷入公報私仇，干涉其他地區內部事務的處境</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n小弟之前已經出過幾個Post，亦做咗唔少嘢先去到呢步，唔該大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.差8.5k就可以對付DQ黃之鋒嘅選舉主任啦，快啲嚟幫手啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1684283/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1684283/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">財政報告</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1c4HVmfnWgjjgUUhzD9vQFXf80XV0Kz1t/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1c4HVmfnWgjjgUUhzD9vQFXf80XV0Kz1t%2Fview&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=5c114c59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1c4HVmfnWgjjgUUhzD9vQFXf80XV0Kz1t/view</a><br />\n<br />\n2.[推爆佢]《香港人權及民主法案》民間制裁名單調查<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1651907/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1651907/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n3.問卷數據<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1pqwDM12O6YdacOJMDXDa8fb6-gNHq1nGmMisMRQQE1Y/edit?usp=drive_open\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1pqwDM12O6YdacOJMDXDa8fb6-gNHq1nGmMisMRQQE1Y%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Ddrive_open&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=1248d555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1pqwDM12O6YdacOJMDXDa8fb6-gNHq1nGmMisMRQQE1Y/edit?usp=drive_open</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌網址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%e3%80%8c%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e5%90%8c%e8%a1%8c%e3%80%8d%e5%80%a1%e5%b0%8e%e8%a8%88%e5%8a%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25e3%2580%258c%25e4%25b8%2596%25e7%2595%258c%25e5%2590%258c%25e8%25a1%258c%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%2580%25a1%25e5%25b0%258e%25e8%25a8%2588%25e5%258a%2583%2F&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=f9246534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%e3%80%8c%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e5%90%8c%e8%a1%8c%e3%80%8d%e5%80%a1%e5%b0%8e%e8%a8%88%e5%8a%83/</a><br />\n希望大家大大力懲罰我！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次嘅問卷調查結果已經Send咗去眾志，solomon yue同埋部分未Co-sponsor嘅美國參議員（參議員方面要填form先交到message所以沒有正式記錄，希望大家信我。雖然我對於回覆呢件事不抱太大期望，盡量做啦唉。）"},{"pid":"0e7cb6ab4953123614bd4033ae789e6e5b78c34a","tid":1696602,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:13:29.000Z","msg":"自推 十連"},{"pid":"cd15bfa25ef5b06dcfee6773c59d43641db451c0","tid":1696602,"uid":157816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:14:03.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"3567d21024c5af7ab2d01b7419333cf0f6209564","tid":1696602,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"9 / 10"},{"pid":"f61b2e52d2df29610dc3305fe5cb6c703bd2187b","tid":1696602,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:15:17.000Z","msg":"8 / 10"},{"pid":"dcca78562f5f4d6dc0aca19ec2dacffbeadddf95","tid":1696602,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:15:27.000Z","msg":"7 / 10"},{"pid":"490f10c3e7ef00591f03dde5412f5ad146deab2e","tid":1696602,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:15:37.000Z","msg":"6 / 10"},{"pid":"471c8c2d24bb8c3394dabb9ebbbf46bc1206960e","tid":1696602,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:15:48.000Z","msg":"5 / 10"},{"pid":"fd1b975c08ffa1308faf9768fe04e78eecdcb53b","tid":1696602,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:16:14.000Z","msg":"BTW 去SOGO啊，一定要去啊<br />\n買買買！"},{"pid":"6c18972f1b01269b274c0ba78d655d9a34c13d21","tid":1696602,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"4 / 10"},{"pid":"f5cfd6a67fede7941a4bf1f39530854e29f4f0bb","tid":1696602,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:16:34.000Z","msg":"3 /10"},{"pid":"e67bafb230edf8e800cf2c156ca6fbc35af8f3e1","tid":1696602,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:16:45.000Z","msg":"2 / 10"},{"pid"